\begin_inset Formula $F_{x}(c\mathbf{u})=cF_{x}(\mathbf{u})$
\end_inset

 for any vectors 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{u}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{v}$
\end_inset

 and scalar 
\begin_inset Formula $c$
\end_inset

, so 
\begin_inset Formula $F_{x}$
\end_inset

 is linear by definition.
